{"id":1573,"date":"2024-01-05T14:04:56","date_gmt":"2024-01-05T14:04:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/?page_id=1573"},"modified":"2024-01-10T09:59:06","modified_gmt":"2024-01-10T09:59:06","slug":"kurumsal","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/kurumsal\/","title":{"rendered":"Kurumsal"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3>KISACA B\u0130Z!<\/h3>\n<p>\u015eirketimiz, 1970 &#8216;den 1996 y\u0131l\u0131na kadar bireysel olarak yap\u0131lan faaliyetlerimiz, 1996 y\u0131l\u0131ndan itibaren de kurumsal olarak hafriyat ve nakliyat a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131kl\u0131 in\u015faat i\u015flerinde <strong>\u00d6Z KO\u00c7AK \u0130N\u015eAAT HAFR\u0130YAT TAAH.NAK. GIDA MAD. T\u0130C. SAN. LTD. \u015eT\u0130<\/strong>. faaliyet g\u00f6stermektedir.<\/p>\n<p>\u0130n\u015faat sekt\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcn vazge\u00e7ilmezi olan alt yap\u0131 ve hafriyat i\u015flerinde T\u00fcrkiye&#8217;nin muhtelif yerlerinde \u00f6nemli projelerin hayata ge\u00e7irilmesinde pay sahibi olan \u015firketimiz ald\u0131\u011f\u0131 her i\u015fi tecr\u00fcbeli personeli ve geni\u015f makine parkuruyla b\u00fcy\u00fck bir gayret ile k\u0131sa zamanda tamamlamaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>\u0130\u015flerimizde g\u00f6sterdi\u011fimiz bu b\u00fcy\u00fck ba\u015far\u0131 i\u015fveren firmalar\u0131n b\u00fcy\u00fck be\u011fenisini kazanm\u0131\u015f ve her zaman referans\u0131m\u0131z olmu\u015ftur.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hizmetlerimiz:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Hafriyat \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Toprak kaz\u0131m\u0131, dolgu i\u015fleri, temel kaz\u0131s\u0131 gibi in\u015faat projelerinde kullan\u0131lan hafriyat i\u015flemleri.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Ta\u015f\u0131mac\u0131l\u0131k (Nakliye) \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> \u0130n\u015faat malzemeleri, toprak, kum, \u00e7ak\u0131l gibi malzemelerin ta\u015f\u0131mas\u0131 ve nakliyesi.<\/li>\n<li><strong>A\u011f\u0131r Ta\u015f\u0131mac\u0131l\u0131k (Nakliye):<\/strong> B\u00fcy\u00fck ve a\u011f\u0131r y\u00fcklerin g\u00fcvenli bir \u015fekilde ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flayan \u00f6zel ta\u015f\u0131mac\u0131l\u0131k hizmeti.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Mobil Konkas\u00f6r Ta\u015f K\u0131rma:<\/strong> Ta\u015flar\u0131 belirli boyutlara \u00f6\u011f\u00fctme veya k\u0131rma amac\u0131yla kullan\u0131lan mobil konkas\u00f6rler arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla ta\u015f k\u0131rma hizmeti.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Stabilize Dolgu \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Zeminin g\u00fc\u00e7lendirilmesi ve istenilen \u00f6zelliklere getirilmesi i\u00e7in stabilize dolgu i\u015flemleri.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Makina Kiralama:<\/strong> \u00c7e\u015fitli in\u015faat makinelerinin kiralama hizmeti, m\u00fc\u015fterilerin projelerinde ihtiya\u00e7 duyduklar\u0131 ekipmanlar\u0131 temin etmelerine yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong>Misyon ve Vizyon:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u00d6z Kocak Hafriyat, m\u00fc\u015fteri memnuniyetini \u00f6n planda tutarak kaliteli, g\u00fcvenilir ve \u00e7evre dostu hizmetler sunmay\u0131 ama\u00e7lamaktad\u0131r. Yenilik\u00e7i yakla\u015f\u0131mlar\u0131, modern ekipmanlar\u0131 ve uzman kadrosuyla sekt\u00f6rde \u00f6nc\u00fc bir firma olma hedefiyle \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>Firma, \u015feffaf i\u015f politikalar\u0131, g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc etik de\u011ferleri ve m\u00fc\u015fteri odakl\u0131 hizmet anlay\u0131\u015f\u0131yla sekt\u00f6rde g\u00fcvenilir bir i\u015f orta\u011f\u0131 olarak \u00f6ne \u00e7\u0131kmaktad\u0131r. \u00d6z Kocak Hafriyat, in\u015faat projelerinin her a\u015famas\u0131nda m\u00fc\u015fterilerine g\u00fcvenilir ve kaliteli hizmet sunarak sekt\u00f6re katk\u0131 sa\u011flamay\u0131 hedeflemektedir.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text] KISACA B\u0130Z! \u015eirketimiz, 1970 &#8216;den 1996 y\u0131l\u0131na k